<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 8. Distribution map of studied Tradescantia L. in the South American domains. Full squares - T. crassula; White squares - T. chrysophylla; Triangles - T. valida; Circles - T. ambigua; Stars - T. boliviana. Light green- Amazon Forest; Orange- Cerrado; Red- Caatinga; Yellow- Chaco and Pantanal; Olive-green- Pampa; Dark green- Atlantic Forest; Purple- Andean Yungas." , "Figure 3. Tradescantia valida G. Brueckn. Holotype of T. valida (B barcode B 100296487). Photograph courtesy of the Botanic Garden and Botanical Museum Berlin-Dahlem, Freie Universitaet Berlin." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/133214" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/133208" .

